- `point`, `grab`, `open_palm`, `fist`
- `pinch_index`, `pinch_middle`, `pinch_ring`, `pinch_pinky`
- `swipe_left`, `swipe_right`, `swipe_up`, `swipe_down`
- `thumbs_up`, `thumbs_down`, `peace_sign`, `ok_sign`
- `rock`, `paper`, `scissors`

